title: QB Andrew Luck making throws in practice for Indianapolis
text:
> Indiana QB Andrew Luck making throws in practice for Indianapolis Indianapolis Colts' Andrew Luck, left, watches his teammates warm up before an NFL football game against the Houston Texans, Thursday, Oct. 8, 2015, in Houston. Luck will miss the game with an injury. (AP Photo/Patric Schneider)
